name: Fishing Stickman[Fishing game]
description:
Not a rhythm game is like a rhythm game, but still a little rhythm game?

The little fishing game [fishing stickman]

[Game Description]

Fishing game Simple Stick is lifting the fish.

Let Tsuriageyo the fish by tapping the screen with timing the overlapping fish on a hook!

It's game over if you miss three times!

It will become more and more difficult with each passing stage.

Please do your best with the aim of all the stages clear.
